{"tid":2171326,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Fb要人做嘢啦: 葉劉又派死亡之吻 - 尖沙咀Sam’s Tailor","createTime":"2020-08-23T23:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T10:47:33.000Z","uid":359125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3941061187ac6b5ef7233e8c9277a2b79de902d8","tid":2171326,"uid":359125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:02:09.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家快啲去比嬲嬲反映返主流意見喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlink:  <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/16720522156/posts/10157485433382157/?extid=XCDxQPkwnpxsoktJ&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F16720522156%2Fposts%2F10157485433382157%2F%3Fextid%3DXCDxQPkwnpxsoktJ%26d%3Dn&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsiiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=e1427231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/16720522156/posts/10157485433382157/?extid=XCDxQPkwnpxsoktJ&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n「日前再到 Sam&lsquo;s Tailor 拜訪第三代掌門人 Roshan Melwani。較早前我到該店並在Roshan建議下，訂做了一套仿照某大牌子款式的粉紅色套裝，想不到數天已起貨，裁剪亦非常貼身及舒適，我對其出品十分滿意。是次穿上新衣到訪， <strong>Roshan 笑說我可以做其「生招牌」並誠邀合照</strong>，其後他建議我再度身訂做新套裝，我也欣然接納。這次他建議用上法國材料，訂造一套不同款式的套裝。<br />\n<br />\n幸好他生性樂觀，正努力為 Sam's Tailor 尋找新商機，<strong>更建議我向特區政府一眾女高官，推銷本地產品(包括他們生產的衣服)，並歡迎她們隨時到店度身訂做套裝。我笑說這是好提議，並一口答應他一試無妨，</strong><br />\n<br />\n其實香港時下女士的服飾大多是現成服裝(ready to wear)，難得Sam's Tailor度身訂做的女裝手工不錯，價錢亦算相宜。如今本地零售市道疲弱，市民消費力大減，<strong>假如一眾特區政府女高官能夠帶頭示範</strong>，身體力行光顧本地產品，支持一流裁縫，相信定能促進本地經濟，為市道打下強心針。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V53dsHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV53dsHJ.jpg&h=d3f22a20&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ygz0R9p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYgz0R9p.jpg&h=da57cfe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00e65c4212e13195e18f21b742c24d1277954576","tid":2171326,"uid":11097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T23:53:19.000Z","msg":"Who？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d10234674d315f046f8804bd534415c3ed8ef79a","tid":2171326,"uid":283071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:34:30.000Z","msg":"Chanel都買唔起咪撚做議員啦<br />\n度身訂造 抄人地個牌子都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe8bf00e4d88702e80b703b973860c98827e172","tid":2171326,"uid":112486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"左邊more"},{"pid":"e4e2f0de1ec76346cb78f06ee9121f593a6be44f","tid":2171326,"uid":128120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T10:47:33.000Z","msg":"香港首個黃色速遞開始左啦！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2170245\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2170245</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}